\[ E(k, m) = k \oplus m \\ D(k, c) = k \oplus c \] <p>一致性方程:  </p> \[ D(k, E(k, m)) = k \oplus (k \oplus m) = (k \oplus k) \oplus m = 0 \oplus m = m \] <p>密钥 k 的长度和明文相等.  </p> <pre><code>template &lt;std::size_t N&gt;
std::bitset&lt;N&gt; E(const std::bitset&lt;N&gt;&amp; key, const std::bitset&lt;N&gt;&amp; plaintext) {
    return key ^ plaintext;
}
</code></pre>
